properties.name: Abdu-Bahodir 2 hotel
properties.desc:
Located in the centre of Samarkand’s old city, Hotel Abdu - Bahodir 2 features an outdoor pool, free Wi-Fi and free private parking.

Rooms here offer air conditioning, a desk, and a private bathroom with a shower.

Other property facilities include a fitness centre and laundry services.

Sherdar Madrasa is a 5-minute walk, and Siab Bazaar is a 15-minute walk away.

Hotel Abdu - Bahodir 2 is 8 km from Samarkand Train Station, and 6 km from Samarkand International Airport.

properties.name: Afrasiab hotel
properties.desc:
Situated in the city centre, Orient Star Kuk-Serai presents both an indoor and an outdoor pools, a sauna and a restaurant; free WiFi in public areas and air-conditioned rooms.

The rooms, suites and apartments all feature a balcony, safety deposit box, a TV with both satellite and cable channels and a refrigerator. A private bathroom comes with a bathtub or a shower, a hairdryer, slippers and free toiletries.

Breakfast is offered every morning and can also be served in the room, and Orient Star Kuk-Serai has both an à la carte and a buffet restaurants and a bar on site. A snack bar is open in the hotel and grocery deliveries and packed lunches can also be requested.

Guests can sunbathe on a sun deck, relax on a terrace, keep in shape in a fitness centre, enjoy massages, laze in shared lounge, have some fun in a nightclub or use the services of a tour desk. A 24-hour front desk is at guests' disposal and so are many other hotel's services.

The Rukhobod Mausoleum can be reached in 5 minutes on foot and the Amir Temur Park is a 1-minute walk away. The Gur-e Amir complex can be visited 550 metres from the hotel. Guests can park their vehicle nearby.

properties.name: Arba Hotel
properties.desc:
For unique experience of lodging in Arba Hotel offers its guests 21 rooms of 5 categories.

Their exclusive design features monochrome décor and fittings, contrasted with vibrantly soft-furnishings and lamps matching the floor palette. Cozy interiors are made of natural materials.

In-room amenities: air-conditioning, Flat Sattelite TV, Wi-Fi internet access, writing desk, mini-bar, WC, personal bathrobe, hairdrier and slippers.

properties.name: Asia Hotel
properties.desc:
Located in Samarkand, 3 km form the historical city centre and a 5-minute walk from Registan Square, Hotel Asia Samarkand features a spa and wellness centre, an outdoor swimming, and a sauna. Guests can enjoy local and international cuisine at the on-site restaurant and café.

The modern rooms here provide guests with an electric kettle, a TV with satellite channels, air conditioning, and a private bathroom with a bath or shower.

Other hotel facilities include a 24-hour front desk, a bar, a fitness centre, meeting or banquet facilities, and a concierge service.

Siab Bazaar is a 7-minute walk, the Registan Ensemble is a 5-minute walk, and the Rukhobod Mausoleum is a 15-minute walk away.

Hotel Asia Samarkand is 7 km from Samarkand Train Station and 5 km from Samarkand International Airport.

properties.name: Astor hotel
properties.desc:
Astor Hotel is located in business district of Samarkand, a 6-minute drive to the historical centre. It features a sauna, hot tub and massage services. Free Wi-Fi is available.

Featuring elegant interiors with bright colours, the rooms are equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV and wardrobe. The bathrooms come with free toiletries, bathrobes and slippers.

Guests can visit the on-site restaurant and taste European cuisine, and it’s possible to order local dishes. Various cafes and restaurants are located a 3-minute walk from Astor Hotel.

Dolphin swimming pool is located a 5-minute walk away. The distance to Samarkand International Airport is 10.5 km from the property.

properties.name: B&B Emir
properties.desc:
Located 5 minutes’ walk from the 15th-century Gur Emir Complex in historic centre of Samarkand city, this family hotel features free Wi-Fi and free water in the lobby.
Guests of B&B Emir benefit from the central location, as Samarkand’s main attractions are within a walking distance from the property. The UNESCO-listed Registan Complex is 10 minutes’ walk away.
Each room at Emir is decorated in a traditional style and includes air conditioning. Bathrooms are fitted with a shower.
A daily breakfast is offered at the Emir’s bar, while several dining options serving national cuisine can be found within a 10-minute walk of the hotel.
A shuttle service to Samarkand Airport (6 km) is provided on request, and guided tours can also be organised by the staff.

properties.name: Bahodir B&B
properties.desc:
B&B Bahodir is located in Samarkand. Free WiFi access is available. At the property you will find a 24-hour front desk, a garden and a shared kitchen.

All rooms feature a garden view. Extras include a desk and a fan.

Other facilities offered at the property include grocery deliveries, a shared lounge and luggage storage. The property offers free parking on site.

Upon request, a shuttle to the airport can be arranged at B&B Bahodir.

properties.name: Bibikhanum Hotel
properties.desc:
Featuring free WiFi and a terrace, Bibikhanum Hotel offers accommodation in Samarkand. Guests can enjoy the on-site restaurant. Free private parking is available on site.

Rooms come with a private bathroom fitted with a shower.

You will find room service at the property.

properties.name: Billuri Sitora hotel
properties.desc:
Featuring free WiFi throughout the property, Hotel Billuri Sitora offers accommodation in Samarkand. Free private parking is available on site.

Each room at this bed and breakfast is air conditioned and features a flat-screen TV. Extras include free toiletries and a hair dryer.

You will find a 24-hour front desk at the property.

properties.name: Caravan Serail
properties.desc:
Located 10 minutes’ walk from the 15th-century Registan Ensemble in Samarkand’s Old Town, this hotel offers a traditional restaurant and rooms with free Wi-Fi. There is also a 24-hour reception.
Set in Samarkand's historical centre, Caravan Serail Hotel provides good access to the main attractions. Bibi-Khanym Mosque is 5 minutes’ walk away, and the 11th-century Shah-i-Zinda Ensemble is 15 minutes’ walk from the hotel.
All rooms at Hotel Caravan Serail feature Oriental décor and come with a satellite flat-screen TV. Bathrooms include a hairdryer.
National cuisine is served in the on-site restaurant with traditional wall patterns. Meals can also be enjoyed on the summer terrace, while watching wall frescos in the courtyard.
Tretiya Banya bus stop is only 50 metres from Hotel Caravan Serail, providing a link to Samarkand Train Station. A transfer is available, and Samarkand Airport is 7 minutes’ drive away.

properties.name: City Hotel
properties.desc:
Free Wi-Fi, a garden and bicycle rental facilities are features of this Samarkand hotel. It is located just a 1-minute walk from Pushkin Library bus stop.

Rooms at the City Hotel offer elegant interiors with wooden furnishings and neutrally coloured decor. A flat-screen TV, wardrobe and telephone are included in every room.

Guests can order food in the hotel’s restaurant, which serves Uzbek and European cuisine. The hotel also has its own bar.

City Hotel is located on Samarkand’s University Boulevard, just a 10-minute walk from Registan Square. In less than 10 minutes’ walk, guests can reach sights like the Gurimir Monument and Alisher Nalayi Museum.

Samarkand Airport and Samarkand Train Station are both located 7 km from the hotel. City Hotel offers free private parking on site.

properties.name: Dilshoda hotel
properties.desc:
Located opposite the ancient Gur-e Amir Mausoleum, this traditional hotel is centrally located in the historic city. A 24-hour reception, garden terrace and homelike accommodation are offered here.

The air-conditioned rooms at Hotel Dilshoda are decorated in patterned fabrics and offer lots of natural light. Complimentary toiletries are provided in the private bathroom.

Guests can sample traditional Uzbek cuisine in the cafés and restaurant just a 10-minute walk away. Breakfast is served each morning and drinks can be also be purchased from Dilshoda’s on-site vending machine.

The ancient Registan Square is only a 5-minute walk from the hotel. Visitors can also explore the 15th-century Ulugh Beg Observatory, which is 5.5 km away.

Transfers to Samarkand Airport can be organised on request. Samarkand Central Train Station is a 10-minute drive from Hotel Dilshoda.

properties.name: Diyor Hotel
properties.desc:
Diyor Hotel offers accommodation in Samarkand. Free private parking is available on site.

Every room includes a private bathroom with a bath and bath or shower, with free toiletries provided. Diyor Hotel features free WiFi .

You will find a shared lounge at the property.

properties.name: Diyora hotel
properties.desc:
Featuring free WiFi and a restaurant, Hotel Diyora offers accommodation in Samarkand. Guests can enjoy the on-site restaurant. Free private parking is available on site.

Rooms have a TV. Some rooms feature views of the pool or city. Every room is equipped with a private bathroom. Extras include slippers and a hair dryer.

You will find a gift shop at the property.
properties.addr: Imam Al Bukhari Street 106, 140110 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Emirkhan Hotel
properties.desc:
Offering a restaurant, Emirkhan Hotel is located in Samarkand, within a 10-minute walk of Samarkand Bus Station. Free WiFi and free private parking are provided.
The air-conditioned rooms are decorated in bright colours and feature a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. The bathroom comes with a hairdryer and free toiletries.
At Emirkhan Hotel you will find a 24-hour front desk and a garden.
Samarkand Train Station is within a 10-minute drive of the property and Samarkand International Airport is 4.5 km away.
Dagbitskaya Street 49, 140120 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Furkat Guest House
properties.desc:
This Samarkand accommodation is located 300 metres from Registan bus stop and Registan Square. It features free Wi-Fi, a garden and a terrace.
Rooms at Furkat Guest House are individually furnished and offer homelike decorations, like colourful quilts. Every room includes a satellite TV, minibar and private bathroom with a hairdryer.
Guests can order meals at the hotel with advance notice. It is possible to eat outside in the garden or on the terrace.
Siabskiy Bazar is located 500 metres from Furkat Guest House. Bibi-Khanym Mosque is only 350 metres away.
Free private parking is available at Furkat Guest House. Samarkand Airport is 6 km from the accommodation, while Samarkand Train Station is 7 km away.

properties.name: Grand Samarkand Superior Hotel
properties.desc: Located in the centre of the ancient city of Samarkand, Grand Samarkand Superior Hotel features a rooftop swimming pool with a sun terrace and loungers, and free Wi-Fi. The classic-style, air-conditioned rooms of this hotel offer elegant, warm-coloured interiors with white brick walls. All rooms come with a flat-screen TV, a refrigerator and a private bathroom with bathrobes and slippers. Grand Samarkand Superior Restaurant is decorated with traditional Uzbek rugs and serves Uzbek and European cuisine. A wide range of wines and fine drinks is offered at the bar. After a day of sightseeing guests can have a massage, relax in the Finnish sauna and swim in the indoor pool. A fitness centre is also available on site. The Old Town District and the famous Registan Square are 2 km from Grand Samarkand Superior Hotel. Samarkand Airport is 10 km away.

properties.name: Hotel Grand Samarkand
properties.desc:
Set in the heart of Samarkand, this hotel offers European cuisine, a garden and free Wi-Fi in public areas. The Old Town district and Registan Square are within a 10-minute drive.
Rooms at the Grand Samarkand offer satellite TV, a minibar and a work desk. They are warmly decorated in a traditional Uzbek style, and include a private bathroom with a hairdryer.
The classically decorated restaurant features an antique piano, and offers a rich variety of à la carte European and Uzbek dishes. A range of drinks and cocktails are also served in the bar, which overlooks the quiet courtyard.
The Guru Amir Mausoleum is 2 km away, and it is 750 metres to the International Museum of Peace and Solidarity.
Both Samarkand Airport and Samarkand Train Station are an 8-minute drive from Hotel Grand Samarkand. A shuttle service is available for an extra fee, and free on-site parking is also offered.
B. Yalangtush Street 38, 140100 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Ideal Hotel
properties.desc:
This hotel enjoys a quiet location in Samarqand, a 5-minute walk from University Boulevard and 10 minutes from the historic Registan Square. Ideal Hotel offers free Wi-Fi and elegant interiors.
The air-conditioned rooms at the Ideal Hotel Samarqand feature classic décor and stylish wooden furniture. All rooms include a flat-screen TV, refrigerator and a terrace.
Breakfast is provided each morning. Uzbek and European dishes are served in the restaurant.
Reception at the Ideal is open 24/7. It includes a tour desk and bicycle rental. A transfer to Samarkand Train Station and Airport is available.
Otahodjaev Street 10, 140143 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Irgashev's Guest House
properties.desc:
Featuring a garden with BBQ facilities, Irgashev’s Guest House is located in Samarkand. Free WiFi access is available at the property. The city centre is 15 minutes’ walk.

A TV is included in each simply furnished guest room. Select rooms have a balcony or terrace with garden views. The private bathrooms have free toiletries.

Airport shuttle service is available at Samarkand Irgashev’s Guest House. The property has a 24-hour front desk. Luggage storage is also offered.

There is a sports arena 2 minutes’ walk from the guest house. The bus station is 2 km away.

properties.name: Jahon Palace Hotel
properties.desc:
This hotel is located in Samarkand, 4 km from the city centre. An outdoor pool, a 24-hour reception and free Wi-Fi in most rooms are featured at Jahon Palace.

The bright, air-conditioned rooms offer warm-coloured interiors and classic-style décor. Each elegant room includes a flat-screen TV, a refrigerator and a private bathroom.

Jahon Restaurant serves Uzbek and European cuisine, and offers buffet breakfast every morning.

The Registan is a 10-minute drive away, and Gūr-e Amīr Mausoleum is an8-minute drive from the hotel.

Samarkand International Airport is 8 km away.

properties.name: Jahongir B&B
properties.desc:
A 5-minute walk from Samarkand city centre, the Jahongir B&B offers free parking and traditional Uzbek cuisine. It has a pretty garden with flowers and a terrace.
Guests stay in colourful, air-conditioned rooms at the Jahongir. Each room has traditional wall decorations, and a private bathroom with shower.
City tours can also be booked at the 24-hour reception.
The historic Registan Square is just a 5-mintue walk from the family-run Jahongir.
Chirokchi Street 4, 140100 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Kamila Hotel
properties.desc: Some quarters from Samarkand’s heart – Registan Square – there is a small and cozy hotel - the Kamila with two courtyards where it is pleasant to relax with a teabowl on trestles or swim in a pool. Away from noisy central streets, the Kamila will afford you an opportunity to enjoy an appeasement and unhasting rhythm of life of Uzbek makhalla (residential quarter). The Hotel motto is “The Guests should feel at home staying far from it”. Actually, it is a real pleasure to take rest in its small but cozy rooms after an eventful day.

properties.name: Konstantin Hotel
properties.desc:
This hotel is located in the north-west of Samarkand, 6 km from the city centre. Free Wi-Fi, indoor and outdoor pools and a gym are featured at Konstantin Hotel.

The bright, air-conditioned rooms offer warm-coloured interiors and classic-style décor. Each elegant room comes with a TV, a refrigerator and a private bathroom with a hairdryer and free toiletries.

The on-site restaurant serves Uzbek and European cuisine, and a selection of drinks is offered at the bar.

Guests can play table tennis and relax in the Turkish steam bath or in the sauna. A children’s playground is available for young guests.

Supermarket Tsum bus stop is a 2-minute walk from Konstantin Hotel. Samarkand International Airport is 9 km away.

properties.name: Lux Hotel
properties.desc:
Located a 10-minute walk from Samarkand’s Old Town district, this hotel features a 24-hour front desk, a bar and free private parking on site. Atakhodzhaeva Street bus stop is 20 metres away.
Rooms at Lux Hotel are individually decorated in bright colours. Each room includes a TV, small refrigerator and a private bathroom with complimentary toiletries.
Breakfast is provided in the hotel’s restaurant, which is decorated in soothing blue colours. Guests can also choose to enjoy meals in their rooms with the hotel's room service.
Abramovski Boulevard is a 2-minute walk from the hotel. Gur Emir Mausoleum is a 15-minute walk away.
Samarkand Airport is a 10-minute drive from Lux Hotel and Samarkand Train Station can also be reached in 10 minutes’ drive. Shuttle services can be arranged upon request.
Atahodzhaeva Street 15, 140100 Samarkand, Uzbekistan
properties.addr: Atahodzhaeva Street 15 (ex Lva Tolstogo Street), 140100 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Majestic Palace Hotel
properties.desc:
The hotel «Majestic Palace» is located in the heart of the city of Samarkand, at the crossroads of the New and the Old City and is conveniently located near the main historical monuments of Samarkand. The hotel has high level of safety, comfortable rooms, a wide range of services for leisure and business meetings, qualified staff will satisfy the most demanding guests. 
Hotel provides all necessary services of European standards, the hotel retains a vivid personality cozy, home away.
The hotel Majestic Palace is a good choice for both business and leisure travelers. Rooms overlooking the inner garden. The warm atmosphere of hospitality awaits guests in beautifully furnished rooms. All rooms include a bathroom with bath, telephone, satellite TV, hairdryer, desk, mini bar, air conditioning. 
There are 36 rooms in the hotel: 4 SINGLE standard rooms, 8 DOUBLE with a wide king size bed and 24 TWIN rooms.
A concierge can help arrange city tours, tickets to museums and theaters, as well as railway and airline tickets. We will do our best to make your stay in our hotel unfogetable.
properties.addr: 32, А Bobur Mirzo street, Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Malika Classic Hotel
properties.desc:
Located 6 minutes’ drive from the Registan in Samarkand, this hotel features a terrace and free parking. It offers air-conditioned rooms with a minibar and a work desk.

All the rooms at Malika Classic Hotel are decorated in a traditional Oriental style and include satellite TV and a safety deposit box. Bathrooms come with a hairdryer.

The Malika’s restaurant with wooden furnishings and Oriental patterns serves national and European cuisine. Meals can be also enjoyed on the terrace.

Set in a business district of Samarkand, Malika Hotel provides good access to the main attractions, such as the Gur-e Amir Complex 5 minutes’ drive away. Shah-i-Zinda Ensemble is 10 minutes’ drive from the hotel.

Samarkand Airport and Train Station are 12 minute’s drive from Malika Classic Hotel, and a shuttle service is available.

properties.name: Malika Prime hotel
properties.desc:
Located 2 minutes’ walk from the Amir Temur Monument and Gur-e Amir Complex in Samarkand, this hotel features a terrace and air-conditioned rooms with a minibar.

Each traditionally decorated room at Malika Prime Hotel has a work desk and satellite TV channels. A hairdryer is provided in the bathrooms.

The Malika’s restaurant with Orient-style design serves national Uzbek cuisine and European specialities. Meals can be enjoyed on the terrace.

Guests of Malika Prime benefit from the central location, as the Registan Ensemble is 15 minutes’ walk away. Samarkand’s Central Park is 12 minutes’ walk from the hotel.

Malika Prime Hotel is 10 minutes’ drive from Samarkand Airport, and a shuttle service is available on request.

properties.name: Mixt Royal Palace
properties.desc:
Located in the city centre of Samarkand and featuring an on-site restaurant, Mixt Royal Palace offers guests a breakfast buffet, free internet access and free private parking.
Rooms at the hotel offer a minibar and refrigerator, an electric kettle, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, air conditioning, and a private bathroom with a shower.
Other property facilities include a snack bar, an on-site mini-market, luggage storage, a bar, a 24-hour front desk, a business centre, meeting facilities, and an airport shuttle.
GUM Shopping Centre is an 8-minute walk, and the Music and Drama Theatre is a 20-minute walk.
Mixt Royal Palace is 6.5 km from Samarkand Train Station and 7 km from Samarkand International Airport.
Amir Temur Street, 33, 140100 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Najiba
properties.desc:
Najiba offers accommodation in Samarkand. Free private parking is available on site.
There is a 24-hour front desk at the property.
Muborak, 83, 140111 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Nodir Samarkand hotel
properties.desc:
Located in Samarkand, 3.5 km from the city centre, Nodir Samarkand features an on-site restaurant and a breakfast buffet. Guests can relax at the hotel’s sauna, swimming pool, and fitness centre.

Rooms here provide guests with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a wardrobe, air conditioning, and a private bathroom with a bath or shower.

Other property facilities include a 24-hour front desk, a bar, a garden, luggage storage, a tour desk, a business centre, room service, and an airport shuttle.

Afrasiyab Settlement Ruins are directly in front of the hotel, less than a 2-minute walk. Olimpia Stadium is 1.5 km away, and Siab Bazaar is 2 km from the hotel.

Nodir Samarkand is 7 km from Samarkand Train Station, and 2 km from Samarkand International Airport.

properties.name: Orient Star Samarkand
properties.desc:
Free Wi-Fi, an outdoor swimming pool and poolside terrace are features of this Samarkand hotel. It is located a 15-minute drive from Samarkand’s historic Old Town district.

Orient Star Samarkand’s rooms include a minibar and satellite TV. Complimentary toiletries and a hairdryer are provided in the private bathroom.

Breakfast is provided in the hotel’s restaurant, which serves both European and regional Uzbek cuisine. Guests can also order room service 24 hours per day, or enjoy a drink at the well-stocked hotel bar.

Registan Square is a 15-minute drive from the hotel. The Old Town’s Bazar and Samarkand’s central park can both be reached within 10 minutes’ drive.

Samarkand Train Station is a 15-minute drive from the hotel, while Samarkand Airport can be reached in just 10 minute’ drive. The hotel can arrange shuttle services upon request.

properties.name: Platan
properties.desc:
This hotel is located in Samarkand, 2 km from Guri Amir and 2.5 km from the Registan. Free Wi-Fi and free parking are available in Platan Hotel.
Rooms here will provide you with a flat-screen TV, air conditioning and cable channels. Featuring a shower, private bathrooms also come with a hairdryer and a bathrobe. You can enjoy a garden view from all the rooms. Extras include a desk, a safety deposit box and a laptop safe.
The on-site restaurant serves Uzbek cuisine, and a variety of drinks is offered at the bar.
At Platan you will find free airport shuttle service and a 24-hour front desk. Other facilities offered include ticket service and a tour desk.
Samarkand Airport is 5 km from the property.

properties.name: Registon Palace Hotel
properties.desc:
In the center of Samarkand, right on the “border” of the city’s historical and business districts there is a luxury 4-star hotel - the Registon Plaza. Impressed by a vast space from the lobby on the ground floor up to the roof itself, the respectful hotel building seems visually even larger when you get inside; all the rooms there are located along the walls and if you look downwards from the upper floor’s corridors you have a feeling as though you are at a cruise liner.

There is an elegant decoration, furniture of good quality and modern facilities in every comfortable and spacious room irrespective of its type.

As it is proper with 4 “stars” the Registon Plaza has a large restaurant, luxury conference hall, swimming pool, fitness center and other services. Staying in this hotel will, certainly, be best remembered for high quality of its services, rest and leisure.

properties.name: Samarkand Dream hotel
properties.desc:
Offering a restaurant, Samarkand Dream Hotel is located in Samarkand, a 15-minute walk from Central Park. Free Wi-Fi access is available.

The accommodation will provide you with a flat-screen TV and air conditioning. There is also a refrigerator. The private bathrooms also come with a hairdryer and free toiletries.

Guests are welcome to visit the on-site restaurant and taste Uzbek and European cuisine.

The distance to Samarkand Airport is 7.5 km from Samarkand Dream Hotel.

properties.name: Samarkand Safar hotel
properties.desc:
Offering an outdoor pool and a sauna, Hotel Samarkand Safar is located in Samarkand, 2.5 km from the Registan. Free WiFi access is available.

Each room here will provide you with a TV, air conditioning and a DVD player. Featuring a bath or shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer and free toiletries. Extras include a CD player, satellite channels and cable channels.

At Hotel Samarkand Safar you will find a 24-hour front desk and a garden. Other facilities offered at the property include a shared lounge and an ironing service. The property offers free parking.

Samarkand International Airport is 6.5 km away.

properties.name: Samarkand Seoul hotel
properties.desc:
Hotel Samarkand Seoul offers accommodation in Samarkand. Guests can enjoy the on-site bar. Free WiFi is provided throughout the property and free private parking is available on site.

There is a shared kitchen at the property.

properties.name: Shaxzoda Lux Hotel
properties.desc:
Shaxzoda Lux is located in Samarkand. With a blend of European and Asian elements, it offers free Wi-Fi, an indoor pool and a sauna. The on-site restaurant serves Italian and Oriental dishes.

All rooms comprise air-conditioning and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. Each unit also provides a safe, minibar and a private bathroom with a shower, hairdryer and free toiletries.

Free private parking is provided. The Central Park is 2.7 km away. A railway station and airport are 10 km from the Shaxzoda.

properties.name: Simxo Hotel
properties.desc:
Featuring free WiFi throughout the property, Hotel "Simxo" offers accommodation in Samarkand. Free private parking is available on site.

Each room at this hotel is air conditioned and is equipped with a flat-screen TV. For your comfort, you will find slippers and free toiletries. A TV with satellite channels is featured.

There is a 24-hour front desk at the property.

properties.name: Sultan Hotel Boutique
properties.desc:
Sultan Hotel Boutique is located in Samarkand and offers a restaurant, a rooftop terrace with stunning views of the surroundings, free WiFi access and rooms with air-conditioning and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels.
All rooms comprise a refrigerator. Featuring a bath or shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer and free toiletries. Extras include a desk and bed linen.
At Sultan Hotel Boutique a 24-hour front desk and meeting and banquet facilities are at guests' disposal. Other facilities offered at the property include luggage storage and consierge service. The property offers free parking.
The Registan with its large square and its three madrasahs and the mausoleum are a 5-minute walk away. A grocery shop can be found 200 metres away and the Marmar Bazar is 300 metres away. 3 restaurants are within 100 metres of the hotel.
University Boulvard 1, 140129 Samarkand, Uzbekistan

properties.name: Temur The Great Hotel
properties.desc:
Timur The Great is a guest house located in Samarkand, the second largest city of Uzbekistan, and it offers accommodation with air-conditioning. Samarkand Train Station is a 15-minute ride away and free private parking is available.

The rooms at Timur The Great are classically decorated and feature patterned carpets. Each comes with a wardrobe, a desk and a bathroom fitted with a shower and a hairdryer. Free WiFi is available in the rooms.

The guest house offers luggage storage, as well as laundry and ironing services. A free airport shuttle can be organised.

Samarkand Airport is a 10-minute drive away and the impressive Bibi-Khanym Mosque is only a 5-minute walk away from Timur The Great.

properties.name: Zarina Hotel
properties.desc:
Featuring free WiFi, an outdoor pool and a seasonal outdoor pool, Hotel Zarina offers accommodation in Samarkand. The hotel has a terrace and views of the garden, and guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant or a drink at the bar. Free private parking is available on site.

Each room at this hotel is air conditioned and features a flat-screen TV. The rooms are equipped with a private bathroom with bath or shower. A TV with satellite channels is available.

There is a 24-hour front desk, hairdresser's, and gift shop at the property.

The hotel also offers bike hire and car hire.
